high_descs: Move to the left and stand in front of the chair with the book on it.
Pick the credit card up from the chair.
Go to the left and then face the lamp to the left.
anns.task_desc: Turn a lamp on with a credit card in hand.

high_descs: Walk to the black chair to the left of the couch.
Pick up the red credit card.
Walk to the lamp to the left of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Look at the credit card in the light.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the chair that is next to the couch.
Pick up the credit card that is sitting on the chair.
Walk over to the floor lamp on your left.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a credit card using the light of a lamp.
